{"tha-ap52:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap52:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap52:0.3":"Cundattheraapadana ","tha-ap52:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap52:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap52:1.3":"Agghiyam karayitvana, ","tha-ap52:1.4":"jatipupphehi chadayim. ","tha-ap52:2.1":"Nitthapetvana tam puppham, ","tha-ap52:2.2":"buddhassa upanamayim; ","tha-ap52:2.3":"Pupphavasesam paggayha, ","tha-ap52:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap52:3.1":"Kancanagghiyasankasam, ","tha-ap52:3.2":"buddham lokagganayakam; ","tha-ap52:3.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap52:3.4":"pupphagghiyamupanayim. ","tha-ap52:4.1":"Vitinnakankho sambuddho, ","tha-ap52:4.2":"tinnoghehi purakkhato; ","tha-ap52:4.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap52:4.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap52:5.1":"‘Dibbagandham pavayantam, ","tha-ap52:5.2":"yo me pupphagghiyam ada; ","tha-ap52:5.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap52:5.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap52:6.1":"Ito cuto ayam poso, ","tha-ap52:6.2":"devasanghapurakkhato; ","tha-ap52:6.3":"Jatipupphehi parikinno, ","tha-ap52:6.4":"devalokam gamissati. ","tha-ap52:7.1":"Ubbiddham bhavanam tassa, ","tha-ap52:7.2":"Sovannanca manimayam; ","tha-ap52:7.3":"Byamham patubhavissati, ","tha-ap52:7.4":"Punnakammappabhavitam. ","tha-ap52:8.1":"Catusattatikkhattum so, ","tha-ap52:8.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap52:8.3":"Anubhossati sampattim, ","tha-ap52:8.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap52:9.1":"Pathabya rajjam tisatam, ","tha-ap52:9.2":"vasudham avasissati; ","tha-ap52:9.3":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap52:9.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap52:10.1":"Dujjayo nama namena, ","tha-ap52:10.2":"hessati manujadhipo; ","tha-ap52:10.3":"Anubhotvana tam punnam, ","tha-ap52:10.4":"sakakammam apassito. ","tha-ap52:11.1":"Vinipatam agantvana, ","tha-ap52:11.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap52:11.3":"Hirannam tassa nicitam, ","tha-ap52:11.4":"kotisatamanappakam. ","tha-ap52:12.1":"Nibbattissati yonimhi, ","tha-ap52:12.2":"brahmane so bhavissati; ","tha-ap52:12.3":"Vangantassa suto dhima, ","tha-ap52:12.4":"sariya oraso piyo. ","tha-ap52:13.1":"So ca paccha pabbajitva, ","tha-ap52:13.2":"angirasassa sasane; ","tha-ap52:13.3":"Culacundoti namena, ","tha-ap52:13.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap52:14.1":"Samanerova so santo, ","tha-ap52:14.2":"khinasavo bhavissati; ","tha-ap52:14.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap52:14.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap52:15.1":"Upatthahim mahaviram, ","tha-ap52:15.2":"anne ca pesale bahu; ","tha-ap52:15.3":"Bhataram me cupatthasim, ","tha-ap52:15.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","tha-ap52:16.1":"Bhataram me upatthitva, ","tha-ap52:16.2":"dhatum pattamhi ohiya; ","tha-ap52:16.3":"Sambuddham upanamesim, ","tha-ap52:16.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap52:17.1":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap52:17.2":"buddho loke sadevake; ","tha-ap52:17.3":"Sandassayanto tam dhatum, ","tha-ap52:17.4":"kittayi aggasavakam. ","tha-ap52:18.1":"Cittanca suvimuttam me, ","tha-ap52:18.2":"saddha mayham patitthita; ","tha-ap52:18.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap52:18.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap52:19.1":"Patisambhidanuppatta, ","tha-ap52:19.2":"Vimokkhapi ca phassita; ","tha-ap52:19.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap52:19.4":"Katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap52:20.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma cundo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap52:21.1":"Cundattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap52:22.1":"Upalivaggo pancamo. ","tha-ap52:23.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap52:24.1":"Upali sono bhaddiyo, ","tha-ap52:24.2":"sannitthapakahatthiyo; ","tha-ap52:24.3":"Chadanam seyyacankamam, ","tha-ap52:24.4":"subhaddo cundasavhayo; ","tha-ap52:24.5":"Gathasatam satalisam, ","tha-ap52:24.6":"catasso ca taduttari. "}